title: Are You Working or Training?
itunes:title: Are You Working or Training?
description:
Episode 507 - Are you getting things done or planning on getting things done? Are you accomplishing your goals or studying about what you should do next? These seem like silly questions but they actually the difference between your success and thinking that you are working towards success when you are just standing still.
